post_text:
Congratulations to the FFA members on a successful Leadership Development Events Season! At State Leadership our 4 competitors all placed!

In Employment Skills Megan Nash placed 1st and Chrissy Stoltenberg placed 8th. Megan will advance to National Competition.

In Extemporaneous Public Speaking Mitchell Vander Wal placed 3rd with a speech on the topic of animal cloning and livestock production.

In Prepared Public Speaking Jessica Boekelheide placed 6th with her speech about the incorporation of hydroponics in the class room environment.
text:
Congratulations to the FFA members on a successful Leadership Development Events Season! At State Leadership our 4 competitors all placed!

In Employment Skills Megan Nash placed 1st and Chrissy Stoltenberg placed 8th. Megan will advance to National Competition.

In Extemporaneous Public Speaking Mitchell Vander Wal placed 3rd with a speech on the topic of animal cloning and livestock production.

In Prepared Public Speaking Jessica Boekelheide placed 6th with her speech about the incorporation of hydroponics in the class room environment.
